creator: Teknobuilt
descriptionHtml:
It is a one stop shop for full regulatory compliance with world safety standards: ISO 45001.It empowers the organisations to measure, manage and move safety beyond zero taking care of mental and social well being of the workforce.
It reduces overheads and enhances safety.PACE HSE gives a bird’s eye view across the organisational operations through a digital safety control tower enabling real-time remote monitoring and faster decision making.It ensures a safe, smart and sustainable future for the world around.
